name: DeadFellaz #595
description: A collection of 10,000 undead NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain. Each unique Deadfella is randomly generated from a combination of over 400 individually drawn traits, including over 50 different outfits. Deadfellaz each have different eyes, noses, mouths, heads and bodies - with no traits explicitly gendered to allow all genders to find representation
